[gd_scene load_steps=56 format=3]

; SKY — Sky-islands archipelago above the clouds.
; Landmarks: Dock Island (spawn, pier + 3 flags + signpost), Stepping
;   Island Chain (9 islands ascending in a spiral), Cloud Bank (walkable
;   cloud platforms), Windmill (tower + 4 blades), Spin Platform (mid-
;   level disc), Boss Pillar (hex pillar with star at summit).
; Secrets: Under-dock alcove (1up + 2 coins), Cloud tunnel with wing cap,
;   Skylight (translucent cloud floor with star below), Red coin trail
;   (8 hardest-reach corners), Pennant chain between islands.
; Tiers: dock (y≈0) / mid-spiral + windmill + clouds (y≈8-18) /
;   summit boss pillar (y≈28-34).

